{"id": "1280492733655679046", "channel_id": "1280443812392472606", "type": 0, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "開場角色，不大可能給到太強(環拉親閨女不算)，不然限定，普池角色，就只能往更OP的方向發展了...", "timestamp": "2024-09-03T11:40:58.108000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1280443812392472606", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "加強朵兒", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1280493568560992346", "channel_id": "1280443812392472606", "type": 19, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "環拉不算開場角，在等級低的情況朵爾現在已經很強了", "timestamp": "2024-09-03T11:44:17.165000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["676337286769672192"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1280492733655679046", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1280443812392472606", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "加強朵兒", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1280495106293497930", "channel_id": "1280443812392472606", "type": 0, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "其實設計上來些小小的改動，就可以很強了！例如：\n外域手術：從虛弱兩回合，變成1+1。\n等價交換：棄牌給回血給盾，不要給總量，變成每棄1張就給一次血+盾。\n這樣配合適當的造物(照片、畫框、我們的家、水手哨、蝴蝶標本)，強度就能直接拉滿。", "timestamp": "2024-09-03T11:50:23.789000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1280443812392472606", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "加強朵兒", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
